  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>Supervisor Responsibilities:</p><p>Making sure employees that report to you meet performance expectations.</p><p>Giving instructions or orders to subordinate employees.</p><p>Ensuring that the work environment is safe, secure and healthy.</p><p>Meeting deadlines.</p><p>Approving work hours.</p><p>Ensure great customer service at all levels.</p><p> Requirements:</p><p>Previous leadership experience.</p><p>Excellent communication skills.</p><p>Eye for detail and accuracy.</p><p>Reliable, with high integrity and strong work ethic.</p><p>Ability to work as part of a team.</p><p>Professional appearance and attitude.</p><p>Computer literacy.</p><p>Proactive organizational skills.</p><p>High school diploma.</p><p>Ability to keep a positive attitude in a fast-paced environment.</p>",
